{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b1bc03b4a9","title":"在民盟省、市委员联席会上的发言","origin":"《鸣放言论（二）》（哈尔滨：“学习生活”编辑室编，1957年7月10日）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"47b161b1cb","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":14,"articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1f125bc955","name":"哈尔滨师范学院"},{"id":"5f4ae20709","name":"关贵武"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a4cafadfef","type":"title","text":"在民盟省、市委员联席会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"},{"id":"a46e0a2ef2","type":"authors","text":"哈尔滨师范学院关贵武","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"},{"id":"537235fe2b","type":"subtitle","text":"（关贵武：民盟省委宣传部长、哈尔滨师范学院讲师）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"},{"id":"6ced317efd","type":"subtitle","text":"六月十四日在民盟省、市委员联席会上的发言","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"},{"id":"882afa9663","type":"paragraph","text":"一、为什么副总理中没有党外人士，而其它行政部门都可以有。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"},{"id":"cf2279b8f9","type":"paragraph","text":"二、报纸上登载了对我发言的指责。我在省政协发言写过稿，原稿有“三三制”，发言前印出来了。以后经过学习修改了。原提“三三制”是在贯彻“长期共存，互相监督”方针里提的，在人事安排中可以考虑。在抗日战争时期，曾实行过“三三制”，这种精神也是不无可取之处。在发言时正式提出已修改了，以现在发言为是。现在批评我主张“三三制”，这种批评是不大妥当的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"},{"id":"fd8e501d8d","type":"paragraph","text":"三、我未受过不白之冤，我发言不是发泄私愤。（市委统战部报来的发言记录整理材料）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9"}],"page":{"id":"5a6581c5ea","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b1bc03b4a9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}